	"TARGET="Curtius"
onMouseOver="return Ebox(INARRAY,LatinRef1,WIDTH,155)"
onMouseOut="nd();">
Curtius, 4.1.11</A>.


<P CLASS="ivy">❦</P>


	<P CLASS="justify">
	<A CLASS="note" ID="note5" HREF="
E/Roman/Texts/Diodorus_Siculus/17D*.html#ref5
"onMouseOver="return Ebox(INARRAY,BackRef,WIDTH,175)"
onMouseOut="nd();">5</A>
Curtius
	<A HREF="
L/Roman/Texts/Curtius/5*.html#1.36
	"TARGET="Curtius"
onMouseOver="return Ebox(INARRAY,LatinRef1,WIDTH,155)"
onMouseOut="nd();">
(5.1.36‑39)
	</A>
gives a lurid description of this entertainment, which he regarded as debauching the army.


<P CLASS="ivy">❦</P>


	<P CLASS="justify">
	<A CLASS="note" ID="note6" HREF="
