E/Roman/Texts/Diodorus_Siculus/17D*.html#ref49
"onMouseOver="return Ebox(INARRAY,BackRef,WIDTH,175)"
onMouseOut="nd();">49</A>
Diodorus does scant justice to the dramatic story of Dareius's flight, over taking, and death; cp. <A HREF="
L/Roman/Texts/Curtius/5*.html#8
	"TARGET="Curtius"
onMouseOver="return Ebox(INARRAY,LatinRef1,WIDTH,155)"
onMouseOut="nd();">Curtius, 5.8‑13</A>;
	<A HREF="
https://www.forumromanum.org/literature/justin/texte11.html#15
	"TARGET="offsite"
