Cephisophon was archon at Athens from July of 329 to June of 328 <SPAN CLASS="small">B.C.</SPAN> The Roman consuls of 331 <SPAN CLASS="small">B.C.</SPAN> were C. Valerius Potitus and M. Claudius Marcellus (Broughton, 1.143).


<P CLASS="ivy">❦</P>


	<P CLASS="justify">
